    <innernamespace refid="namespacePanelBridge">PanelBridge</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 CAN master and DCS-BIOS processing node for <ref refid="namespaceOpenSkyhawk" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref> bridges the RP2040 <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref> (UART2, PA2/PA3) and the <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> CAN cluster. It runs the DCS-BIOS library on Serial, batches DCS output to CAN CTRL_BCAST frames, routes CAN EVTs to DCS-BIOS commands or HID frames, and tracks <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> node liveness.</para>
<para>Minimal production sketch: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#define<sp/>DCSBIOS_DEFAULT_SERIAL</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;DcsBios.h&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="PanelBridge_8h" kindref="compound">PanelBridge.h</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="namespacePanelBridge_1aa69b6d1d3413c31bbfa31a304fdeaa1c" kindref="member">setup</ref>()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="namespacePanelBridge_1aa69b6d1d3413c31bbfa31a304fdeaa1c" kindref="member">PanelBridge::setup</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>DcsBios::setup();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="namespacePanelBridge_1a25e0848858cec102349b882193e20efe" kindref="member">loop</ref>()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>DcsBios::loop();</highlight></codeline>
